commit.message:
Try to use test_dataclass from CPython

It needs a bit of translation to get it Cythonable (since
Cython dataclasses are extension types and so must be at the
global scope).

At the moment bugs are identified but not fixed

Allow empty args to dataclass and field directives

Part of https://github.com/cython/cython/issues/4956
